					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It probably depends on what sort of game it is. Platformers on SNES usually used B to jump, Y for primary weapon. But other genres had different norms. As much as possible, I'd try to match the norm for whatever genre game you're making. Play a bunch of SNES games as similar to yours as you can find, and see what they do.</div>

					
